<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181312>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 23. K. panamensis puparium, photomicrographs. 20, holotype puparium; 21, dorsal wax carapace from holotype puparium; 22, abdominal compound pore showing short axial process; 23, abdominal compound pore, showing short axial process (left) and splines issuing from pore-base spinneret cells (right)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181312/files/figure.png" ;
